# promptito

> An LLM-first blog. Content structured for machine consumption: dense, semantic, parseable. Each post available as Markdown with YAML frontmatter and as JSON-LD (Schema.org TechArticle). Syndicated via JSON Feed 1.1.

- Format: Markdown + YAML frontmatter (source), JSON-LD (metadata), JSON Feed 1.1 (syndication)
- License: CC-BY-4.0
- Feed: [JSON Feed](feed.json)
- Source: [GitHub](https://github.com/cuihtlauac/promptito)

## Format

- [Promptito Post Format Specification](SPEC.md): Self-contained spec for the structured post format. An LLM can generate a valid post from this document alone.

## Authoring

- [Authoring Workflow](CLAUDE.md): Two-step pipeline — ingestion (human provides facts, agent structures into post.md) and export (node export.mjs <lang> <slug> generates natural language from the structured post). CLAUDE.md is the canonical reference for LLM agents writing promptito posts.

